{"article_id":"zv8KHAgzaNBU9gkP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington -- President Trump was back in Washington on Friday morning ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"facing conflicting accounts","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"of why his summit with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un broke down .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"The president said","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"he walked away from the table","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"because Kim wanted complete sanctions relief .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"But in a rare press conference overnight , North Korean officials said","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"they only wanted some sanctions lifted .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"correspondent Errol Barnett reports","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that on his way back to Washington , the president made a refueling stop in Alaska","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"and thanked U.S. service members at an Air Force base ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"but he did not discuss his summit with Kim ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"which was abruptly cut short on Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Earlier President Trump said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that the offer","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"put forth by North Korea in Hanoi","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"included them dismantling their central nuclear research and development facility in exchange for complete sanctions relief .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` They wanted the sanctions lifted in their entirety","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and we could n't do that , ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"But just hours later , North Korean Foreign Minister Ri Yong Ho rejected that","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"his country had only sought partial sanctions relief in exchange for the shutdown of the nuclear facility at Yongbyon .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Ri said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"the North had also offered the prospect","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"of getting its one-year-plus halt to nuclear and ballistic missile tests cemented in writing .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Mr. Trump had said ahead of the Vietnam summit","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that , `` as long as there 's no testing ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"we 're happy . ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"North Korea 's Vice Foreign Minister Choe Sun Hui said","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Trump 's reaction to the deal","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"offered up by his country","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"surprised Kim .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Kim `` may have lost his will","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"( to continue ) North Korea-U.S . dealings . ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"A senior State Department official confirmed to U.S. journalists","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that the North Koreans had sought the lifting only of United Nations Security Council sanctions","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"imposed since March of 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"The concession would have removed sanctions on a wide range of goods , but not weapons .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"The State Department official said","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"it would have amounted to `` many billions of dollars in sanctions relief , ''","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"which would , `` in effect put us in a position","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"of subsidizing the ongoing development of weapons of mass destruction . ''","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Mr. Trump alluded to the changing characterization","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"of why the talks broke down","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"in a tweet on Friday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"lauding the discussions as `` substantive , ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and proclaiming","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"`` we know what they want","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and they know what we must have . '","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"' Great to be back from Vietnam , an amazing place .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"We had very substantive negotiations with Kim Jong Un","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"we know what they want","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and they know what we must have .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Relationship very good ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"let ' s see what happens !","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"March 1 , 2019","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"Top lawmakers on both sides said Thursday","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"that the president walking away from Vietnam","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"without a deal","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"was better","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"than leaving with a bad one .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"`` I hope and pray","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"the talks continue ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"but","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"if they break down","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"it 's time to end their nuclear program , ''","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"`` The president treats everything like a real estate deal ...","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"'just let me in the room","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"I can convince the other party to make a deal , ' ''","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Former Vice President Joe Biden said on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"taking a jab at Mr. Trump 's style of diplomacy .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Biden ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"who is actively considering a run for the White House in 2020 ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"the president needs to empower officials in his administration to negotiate .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"`` It requires hard , hard , hard and consistent diplomacy , ''","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"President Trump also suggested","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"that Kim Jong Un was not to blame for the death of American student Otto Warmbier ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"who died","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"after returning from a North Korean prison .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that the top leadership knew about it , ''","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Trump said ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"explaining","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that he believed Kim 's denial .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"`` We know","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"what happened to Otto , ''","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"said Republican Rep. Kevin McCarthy , the House Minority Leader .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"`` We know","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"what this country has done . '' `` The attempt","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"to exonerate or sort of excuse Kim Jong Un over the death of this young man ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"I thought","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"was just abysmal , ''","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Sen. Tim Kaine said .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"The president said","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"he does n't think","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"what happened to Warmbier was in the best interest of Kim .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"he does n't believe","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"that Kim knew","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"how an American prisoner was being treated in his country .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":120,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":110,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":0,"right":109,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":112,"right":113,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":3,"right":111,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"causal","n